Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,0:01:26.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}除此之外别无他求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:27.62,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}Catch you
